{"tid":1759254,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對住下年立法會選舉，除左要唸點贏，仲有一樣野一定要做","createTime":"2019-11-27T14:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T14:09:18.000Z","uid":295459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40e88c24373c1fbaca9d23ca6e93d1d2d0c8556a","tid":1759254,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"就係雙普選中其中一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>普選立法會所有議席呀</strong></span></span><br />\n而家連外國都極關注我地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要不停提呢樣野</span></strong></span><br />\n我地仲有一年時間<br />\n<br />\n區議會果D爭取大眾支持<br />\n我地係到口嗡嗡係冇用架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好當班區議員係傻</strong></span></span><br />\n我地有睇嘅片，佢同佢班助理一定都有睇<br />\n而我地係到講佢地要做乜要做乜係冇用，除非你直頭落去幫佢手做<br />\n唔係落去幫手嘅，除左登記選民之外<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該一齊出黎爭取立法會普選</span></span><br />\n最終達成五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n而家我地需要用一年時間瘋狂爭取立法會普選<br />\n不停吸引眼球<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">盡量一招用兩三次就夠</span></strong><br />\n唔好用死一招<br />\n<br />\n我見到一堆立會規則內點贏嘅PO 事實係OK唔錯<br />\n唔少都好高質<br />\n但係一直講左咁耐雙普選<br />\n點解唔爭取呢<br />\n唔該比更多骨氣出黎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7504a351d94d5dfe602c9bb39d93ebe39c3878c","tid":1759254,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"P牌<br />\n推唔到<br />\n求推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03957b82e49724d5b70a0f4e88b02f96be3d0cc","tid":1759254,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"提提你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一人一票好處就係咁喇<br />\n<br />\n要求落實全面雙普選"},{"pid":"3f65d7d1a7a255ed3f10d21e8db653b85797dd04","tid":1759254,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一人一票贏撚到開行果時<br />\n緊係要爭取立會都一人一票啦<br />\n有冇搞錯呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}